# AI Agent Agency - .gitignore
# =============================
# Framework for AI agent teams that audit and maintain codebases.
# Local project customizations coexist with the public framework.

# Audit reports (generated locally per project)
audits/*.md
audits/*.log
!audits/.gitkeep

# Dated audit archives (local only)
audits/*-20[0-9][0-9]-*.md

# Claude Code context (user-specific session data)
.claude/

# VSCode user settings (workspace-specific, not the .code-workspace file)
.vscode/

# Operating system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor backup files
*~
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak

# Node modules (if scripts use npm)
node_modules/

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Environment files (contain local paths)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Agent images (large binary files, deploy separately)
agents/images/*.jpg
agents/images/*.png
agents/images/*.webp
!agents/images/.gitkeep

# -------------------------------------------
# TRACKED FILES (pushed to GitHub)
# -------------------------------------------
# - agents/*.md (agent profiles — useful as real-world examples)
# - agents/templates/ (blank agent template)
# - .config/mcp_agents.json (production configuration example)
# - .config/mcp_agents.example.json (clean template for new projects)
# - ai-agent-agency.code-workspace (penthouse studio VS Code theme)
# - docs/ (documentation, guides, optimization ideas)
# - templates/ (agent templates)
# - examples/ (working example agents)
# - scripts/ (audit utilities and templates)
# - README.md (public-facing introduction)
